    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "First thing: if we want to pack translations to the binary app there is solution to generate temporary .qrc files with compiled .qm-files. Usage (cmake):\r\n```\r\n# Create translations QRC file from .ts files\r\nfile(GLOB TS_FILES \"translations/*.ts\")\r\ntr_to_qrc(\"${CMAKE_CURRENT_BINARY_DIR}/some_name.qrc\")\r\n\r\n# Generate \r\nqt5_add_resources(QRC_SOURCES ${QRC_FILES} )\r\n\r\n# Compile\r\ntarget_sources(${PROJECT_NAME} PRIVATE ${QRC_SOURCES})\r\n```\r\n[TrToQrc.cmake.txt](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/files/8671460/TrToQrc.cmake.txt)\r\n",
